Chopper is a main character in the One Piece franchise. He is a reindeer-human hybrid who gained human intelligence after eating a Devil Fruit called the Human-Human Fruit (ヒトヒトの実, Hito Hito no Mi). Chopper is a toddler-sized human/reindeer hybrid, but his Devil Fruit abilities allow him to change his appearance depending on the situation. He serves as the medical doctor of the Straw Hat Pirates, a group of pirates led by Monkey D. Luffy. Chopper is known for his kind heart, his skills as a doctor, and his ability to transform into different forms to adapt to different situations.
